name: Japanese Tram Iyotetsu, Matsuyama City, Ehime Prefecture
description: This photo was taken 2 years ago when I was an intern in Japan. right in the 2nd year, I tried something new that I had never learned before, namely taking pictures using an analog camera. This photo is a Japanese tram, vacationing in the city with a Japanese tram, vacation feels more enjoyable because it is far from traffic jams and simple. oh no, the more you look at it, the more I miss the atmosphere in Japan lol
